  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/090f634591ae9db8b2c073ffad7e6c55.poster.avif?t=1732055459\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/090f634591ae9db8b2c073ffad7e6c55.webm?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/090f634591ae9db8b2c073ffad7e6c55.mp4?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/8f359c9c68f004371af6a63f243e2988.avif?t=1732055459\" width=608 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an absurd yet thought-provoking journey with <strong><i>Flat Fat Fartfest</i></strong>, a game that tests not only your patience and skill but also the resilience of your  will. Meet <strong>Chuggy</strong>, a determined soul on a quest to conquer a formidable mountain of obstacles—all while grappling with the primal urge for release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/9f35f1aa3bb5a4b34d00978675b9c2d6.poster.avif?t=1732055459\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/9f35f1aa3bb5a4b34d00978675b9c2d6.webm?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/9f35f1aa3bb5a4b34d00978675b9c2d6.mp4?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/6be34cd94d716703dd5a023bac8e56d0.avif?t=1732055459\" width=608 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your ultimate goal is to guide your little fat boy to the mountain's summit, where he can <strong>finally attain the much-desired relief</strong>. But the journey is far from simple—a lot of Karens will appear on your way…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/eb373e8da5500d3d80209a87fcabc494.poster.avif?t=1732055459\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/eb373e8da5500d3d80209a87fcabc494.webm?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/eb373e8da5500d3d80209a87fcabc494.mp4?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you prepared to assume control and assist <strong>Chuggy</strong> in completing his quest? Or will you surrender to the chaos, allowing him to tumble back to the starting point? The choice lies within you, in this uproarious yet <strong>deeply symbolic ascent to the top!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/8966c07ee2f6c34b4f6e01784404ea51.poster.avif?t=1732055459\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/8966c07ee2f6c34b4f6e01784404ea51.webm?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/8966c07ee2f6c34b4f6e01784404ea51.mp4?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/090f634591ae9db8b2c073ffad7e6c55.poster.avif?t=1732055459\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/090f634591ae9db8b2c073ffad7e6c55.webm?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/090f634591ae9db8b2c073ffad7e6c55.mp4?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/8f359c9c68f004371af6a63f243e2988.avif?t=1732055459\" width=608 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an absurd yet thought-provoking journey with <strong><i>Flat Fat Fartfest</i></strong>, a game that tests not only your patience and skill but also the resilience of your  will. Meet <strong>Chuggy</strong>, a determined soul on a quest to conquer a formidable mountain of obstacles—all while grappling with the primal urge for release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/9f35f1aa3bb5a4b34d00978675b9c2d6.poster.avif?t=1732055459\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/9f35f1aa3bb5a4b34d00978675b9c2d6.webm?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/9f35f1aa3bb5a4b34d00978675b9c2d6.mp4?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/6be34cd94d716703dd5a023bac8e56d0.avif?t=1732055459\" width=608 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your ultimate goal is to guide your little fat boy to the mountain's summit, where he can <strong>finally attain the much-desired relief</strong>. But the journey is far from simple—a lot of Karens will appear on your way…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/eb373e8da5500d3d80209a87fcabc494.poster.avif?t=1732055459\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/eb373e8da5500d3d80209a87fcabc494.webm?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/eb373e8da5500d3d80209a87fcabc494.mp4?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you prepared to assume control and assist <strong>Chuggy</strong> in completing his quest? Or will you surrender to the chaos, allowing him to tumble back to the starting point? The choice lies within you, in this uproarious yet <strong>deeply symbolic ascent to the top!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/8966c07ee2f6c34b4f6e01784404ea51.poster.avif?t=1732055459\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/8966c07ee2f6c34b4f6e01784404ea51.webm?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216700/extras/8966c07ee2f6c34b4f6e01784404ea51.mp4?t=1732055459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
